# Bible Reading Plan - Cursor Rules

## Week File Format Requirements

Each week file should follow this structure:

### File Header
- Start with `## [Week Theme Title]` as the main heading
- Follow with a short sentence encapsulating the week's overarching theme

### Daily Entries Format
Each day should follow this exact format:

```
### Day X

[Short theme sentence encapsulating the day's reading]

>"[Scripture quote]" ([Book Chapter:Verse])

 [Read [Book Chapter]](https://www.bible.com/bible/114/[BOOK_ABBREV].[CHAPTER].NKJV)
```

